To write instructions for setting up a water heater with photos and without knowing them:

1. Fara a fita gidan kwallon gizo da aka samu a cikin baki mai amfani.
2. Kar a goge wani baki mai amfani da kuma jefa shi a matsayin hadewa, idan aka sanya shi.
3. Duba cikin baki mai amfani, za a iya duba alamar yanar gizo da aka shirya a cikin shi.
4. Shekar da yanar gizo a cikin baki mai amfani, a zama ya fi hoton shi.
5. Kar a goge wani baki mai amfani da aka samu a cikin baki mai amfani.
6. Jefa baki mai amfani a matsayin hadewa, sannan duba cikin baki mai amfani domin za ka iya duba yanar gizo da aka shirya a cikin shi.
7. Kar a goge wani baki mai amfani da aka samu a cikin baki mai amfani.
8. Jefa baki mai amfani a matsayin hadewa, sannan duba cikin baki mai amfani domin za ka iya duba yanar gizo da aka shirya a cikin shi.
9. Kar a jefa shi a matsayin hadewa, sannan kuma duba hotunan yanar gizo a cikin baki mai amfani.
10. Idan an samu hotunan yanar gizo a cikin baki mai amfani, za ka iya fita yanar gizo a shekara.
11. Duba cikin baki mai amfani domin za ka iya duba alamar yanar gizo da aka shirya a cikin shi.
12. Kar a jefa baki mai amfani a matsayin hadewa.
13. Tsirara yanar gizo a cikin baki mai amfani sannan duba hotunan yanar gizo a cikin baki mai amfani domin za ka iya
